description.en:
OPCX is a POS 3.0 multifunctional masternode coin, built on a solid foundation from which we can extensively build our products.

The future of OPC is brought to you by the power of X!
With OPCX swap, you get a coin return instead of a coin burn.

OPCX is powered by the Revolutionary technology of POS 3.0 along with an enhanced Masternode system, one that far exceeds the possibilities of the older version. OPCX is bringing in the next wave of OverPowered Coin investment and going to scopes beyond the limitations it once had.

The Future of not only OPC but also POS delivery is here today! With POS 3.0 it offers 6 hour coin maturity, meaning SAME DAY STAKING! Don't be stuck in the past with yesterday's technology, join this wave into the future!
